Results.Description:
Run a limited beta to get customer feedback on our Solr Search Service.

Acceptance Criteria
  • Create beta hive on Agile Commons - use Backlog page beta hive for reference
  • Determine how long the beta will run
  • Provide a way for beta users to access the Solr Search Service
  • Identify beta users
  • Engage beta users
  • Collect feedback
  • Close down the beta
  • Send a thank you to users - Katrina did cookies I think
  • Search must be highly available - hardware issues or index issues must not cause the search service to be down for more than xminutes.
